Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:22:06.38,ED-JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}潮風に溶けた面影は幻のままで今も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.67,0:22:14.22,ED-JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}リアルで鮮明な思い出は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:19.18,ED-JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}何度も何度も繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:27.02,ED-JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}嘘でもいいからそばにいてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.02,0:22:31.78,ED-JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}もっと近くで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:37.45,ED-JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}すぐ好きになって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.45,0:22:40.25,ED-JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}時間だけが過ぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:45.88,ED-JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}あぁ…戻りたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:54.97,ED-JP2,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)}失恋ソング沢山聴いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:23:02.64,ED-JP2,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)}泣いてばかりの私はもう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.64,0:23:05.40,ED-JP2,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)}捨てたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.85,0:23:08.61,ED-JP2,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)}強がらないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:13.49,ED-JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}素直になってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.53,0:23:19.37,ED-JP2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}なんて遅いよね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:22:06.38,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}你的面容随海风飘散彷如幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.67,0:22:14.22,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}可记忆却如此鲜明难以忘却
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:19.18,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}一次又一次反复
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:27.02,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}请待在我身边 谎言也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.02,0:22:31.78,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}再近一些
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:37.45,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}就这样陷入爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.45,0:22:40.25,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}只剩时间流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:45.88,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}想要回归
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:54.97,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)}听过太多失恋的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:23:02.64,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)}总是哭泣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.64,0:23:05.40,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)}也想要不管不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.85,0:23:08.61,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)}不必逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:13.49,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}坦率一些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.53,0:23:19.37,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}却为时已晚
